    "Additionally, the self-attention approach directly captured intra-sentence dependencies on the joint model.",
    "They showed the results on two benchmark datasets on joint model significantly and consistently which surpass the current technique.",
    "Lotfy et al. [86] examined the extra features that has been improved the overall performance for all the embedding models when it was created to a BiLSTM-CRF NER model using AreBert embedding.",
    "This feature achieved the accuracy with 79.48% on AQMAR corpus and 86.71% of F1-score.",
    "The authors also analyzed model's failures to assess the limits of employing deep learning by using Bert embedding in NER."
